ol.li: For wind Region D, site wind classification is given according to the distance (km) from the smooth boundary (coastline or higher wind region).

This Table includes revisions to wind classifications for wind Region D that take into account the Western Australia State Variation to NCC 2022 which changes the ARI Importance Level 2 from 1:500 to 1:1000.
